Que: Micro service architecture performance issue:-
Ans : Below are some problem/solution for performace related issue.
Fault tolerance:	
Slow service blocks upstream thread pools -> Circuit breaker (Resilience4j) to fail fast
Misconfigured timeouts exhaust resources  -> Bulkhead pattern isolates thread pools
Retry storms amplify load on degraded services -> Exponential backoff with jitter prevents storms
No isolation between downstream dependencies -> Propagate deadline budgets across calls	
Network & latency	
Blocking synchronous calls reduce throughput  ->  BFF pattern to fetch exactly what's needed(Graph QL)
Chained calls accumulate latency ->	              Async messaging (Kafka, RabbitMQ) to decouple
Central load balancer becomes a bottleneck ->     Consistent hashing to spread traffic evenly
Data mangmnet 
Distributed transactions are slow and complex -> Materialized views per service to avoid joins


